{"word":"G2184 - ἐφήμερος - ephḗmeros - ef-ay'-mer-os - Daily","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἐφήμερος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">ephḗmeros</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ef-ay'-mer-os</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Daily</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"அநுதின - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"1. lasting for a day"},{"paragraph":"2. daily"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1909 - ἐπί - epí - ep-ee'/1909\">G1909</a> and <a href=\"#/G2250 - ἡμέρα - hēméra - hay-mer'-ah/2250\">G2250</a>; <i>for a day</i> (&ldquo;ephemeral&rdquo;), that is, <i>diurnal:</i> - daily.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}